==========================================
HTTP/1.1 201 Created
Content-Length: 0
Location: /v2/subscriptions/REGEX([0-9a-f]{24})
Fiware-Correlator: REGEX([0-9a-f\-]{36})
Date: REGEX(.*)



02. Create entity with status=off (not notif)
=============================================
HTTP/1.1 201 Created
Content-Length: 0
Location: /v2/entities/E1?type=T
Fiware-Correlator: REGEX([0-9a-f\-]{36})
Date: REGEX(.*)



03. Update entity to status=on (notif)
======================================
HTTP/1.1 204 No Content
Fiware-Correlator: REGEX([0-9a-f\-]{36})
Date: REGEX(.*)



04. Update entity to status=fail (not notif)
============================================
HTTP/1.1 204 No Content
Fiware-Correlator: REGEX([0-9a-f\-]{36})
Date: REGEX(.*)



05. Update entity to status=on (notif)
======================================
HTTP/1.1 204 No Content
Fiware-Correlator: REGEX([0-9a-f\-]{36})
Date: REGEX(.*)



